Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:29.73,文泉中1080HDR,,0,0,0,,黄昏鸟更敏捷\N{\r文泉英1080HDR}{\i1}Hesperornis{\i} is more agile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:49.12,文泉中1080HDR,,0,0,0,,但在X鱼眼中 万物皆可餐\N{\r文泉英1080HDR}But in the eyes of an X-fish,anything is on the menu...
