Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:29.08,文泉中1080HDR,,0,0,0,,海洋中的危险不仅仅只来自致命的猎手\N{\r文泉英1080HDR}Danger in the oceandoesn't only come from deadly hunters.
