Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.37,0:30:34.00,文泉中1080HDR,,0,0,0,,史前地球的陆地由恐龙统治\N{\r文泉英1080HDR}The lands of the prehistoric planetwere ruled by the dinosaurs.
