Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.15,0:31:06.32,文泉中1080HDR,,0,0,0,,锥形的嘴 粗糙的皮肤 长着四个鳍而不是四肢\N{\r文泉英1080HDR}Tapered snout, rough skin,four fins instead of normal limbs
