Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.73,0:31:45.86,文泉中1080HDR,,0,0,0,,在现代世界诸如鳄鱼的爬行类动物拥有这种能力\N{\r文泉英1080HDR}In the modern world, we seethis ability in reptiles like crocodiles.
