Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.92,0:32:04.84,文泉中1080HDR,,0,0,0,,鉴于沧龙是爬行类动物、是蜥蜴\N{\r文泉英1080HDR}{\i1}Mosasaurus{\i}, given that they're reptiles,given that they're lizards,
