Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.60,0:33:42.85,文泉中1080HDR,,0,0,0,,以确保结果正确\N{\r文泉英1080HDR}to ensure they were correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.85,0:33:45.27,文泉中1080HDR,,0,0,0,,{\an8}(尾部长度)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.27,0:33:49.19,文泉中1080HDR,,0,0,0,,四次不同的测试得出了相同的总体结论\N{\r文泉英1080HDR}All four of the different trialscame to the same overall conclusion.
